<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. يُخْفِي مَخَازِي الْجَهْلِ وَالْعِصْيَانِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَرُؤُوسُ سُوءٍ لا اهْتِمَامَ بِهِمْ بِدِيـ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>نٍ قَامَ أَوْ قَدْ خَرَّ لِلأَذْقَانِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَلَرُبَّمَا أَبْدَوْا عِنَايَتَهُمْ بِهِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>بِسِيَاسَةٍ تَخْفَى عَلَى الإِنْسَانِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>تَعْسًا لِمَنْ أَضْحَى يُتَابِعُ قَوْلَ مَنْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>بَخَسَ الْهُدَى وَمَزِيَّةَ الأَذْهَانِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>تَرَكُوا هِدَايَةِ رَبِّهِمْ وَرَسُولِهِمْ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>هَذَا وَرَبِّكَ غَايَةَ الْخُذْلانِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>حُرِمُوا هِدَايَةَ دِينِهِمْ وَعُقُولِهِمْ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>هَذَا وَرَبِّكَ غَايَةَ الْخُسْرَانِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>تَرَكُوا هِدَايَةَ رَبِّهِمْ فَإِذَا بِهِمْ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>غَرْقَى مِن الآرَاءِ فِي طُوفَانِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَتَفَرَّقُوا شِيَعًا بِهَا عَنْ نَهْجِهِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>مِنْ أَجْلِهَا صَارُوا إِلَى شَنْآنِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>كُلٌّ يَرَى رَأْيًا وَيَنْصُرُ قَوْلَهُ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَلَهُ يُعَادِي سَائِرَ الإِخْوَانِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَلَوْ أَنَّهُمْ عِنْدَ التَّنَازُعِ وُفِقُوا<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>لَتَحَاكَمُوا للهِ دُونَ تَوَانِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَلأَصْبَحُوا بَعْدَ الْخِصَامِ أَحِبَّةً<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>غَيْظَ الْعِدَا وَمَذَلَّةَ الشَّيْطَانِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>